ul.li:
List the network details for a datacenter
 Shows the persisted network details for a
            datacenter in the
            vCenter.# eon list-network-info -vcenter-id <vCenter ID> --datacenter-name <Datacenter Name>
where:

vCenter ID - ID of the vcenter containing the cluster.

Datacenter Name - Datacenter name of the vCenter where the clusters (to be used
                for compute resource) resides.

Example
            Output:# eon list-network-info -vcenter-id BC9DED4E-1639-481D-B190-2B54A2BF5674 --datacenter-name DC1
